high_descs: turn to the right and go forward a few steps and turn to the right and go to the counter
pick up the right candle from the toilet tank
turn to the right and take a step and turn to the left facing the sink counter
put the candle on the counter top in front of the sink
turn to the right twice and take a step and turn to the right and go to the wall and turn to the right facing the toilet
pick up the candle from the toilet tank
turn to the right and take a few steps and turn to the left and go to the sink counter
put the candle on the counter top behind the other candle
anns.task_desc: Place two candles on the sink counter top

high_descs: Turn to the left and walk forward then turn to the right and walk forward to the toilet.
Pick up the leftmost candle from the back end of the toilet.
Turn to the left and then back to the counter.
Set the candle on the counter
Turn around completely and walk to your left. Make a right and face the toilet.
Pick up the candle on the back end of the toilet.
Turn to the right and walk to the counter.
Set the candle next to the other candle on the counter.
anns.task_desc: Put two candles on the counter.

high_descs: Turn right and walk to the counter to the right of the toilet.
Pick up the yellow candle to the right of the soap bottle on the toilet tank lid.
Take a step right.
Place the candle on the counter in front of the left sink basic, all the way to the left.
Take a couple steps left, back to the toilet.
Pick up the candle on top of the toilet tank.
Take a step right, back to where you put the first candle.
Place the candle on the counter behind the other candle.
anns.task_desc: Place two candles on a counter.
